<br />
That's a ridiculous point. If you can find pot and ecstasy, you can easily find harder drugs. As someone who, in the past, did quite a bit of illegal substances I will just tell you that if you can find illegal drugs, you are only a stone's throw away from finding illegal firearms. There is a fair bit of overlap in those areas already. It would actually have been cheaper for me to purchase a firearm illegally than legally.<br />
<br />
Then again, I suppose that is only based on my personal experience and it varies for others.</div>
