</div>My point was that there IS still a barrier of some kind.  Not everyone is going to be able to easily find illegal guns to purchase.  Right now I could get my hands on multiple guns within minutes since it's so easy to legally obtain them.  But illegal guns and hard drugs?  That would require some work, especially in this podunk town.</div>
