I think the thing with the drugs to weapons analogy is mainly this: these guys who do these shootings? Are they really the types who know the type of people to get a hold of illegal drugs? They generally seem less on the borderline criminal element side and more on the 'oh yeah, that crazy loner dweeb guy who's a really good student but has no friends because he weirds people out' side.</div>
