</div>That's because that's the stance of the most vocal gun control groups.  I'm personally in favor of stricter gun control laws, but the big question is how we make them more restrictive without making illegal firearm sales more appealing than legal ones.<br />
<br />
<div align="center" style="margin:5px; margin-top:5px; ">
<table width="85%" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#333333" class="bbcodeQUOTE">
  
