<br />
I believe that the fault lies with both the individual and society as a whole.  Society should do their best to prevent and respond to mental illness, but when these measures fail we should do our best to determine the cause of the action and how to respond to it on a case-by-case basis.  If we determine that it was the individual at fault then they should be held responsible for it.<br />
